channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: 1 dead, 2 missing in 'major marine incident' off Connecticut coast
item.description: One person is dead and two are missing with several others injured in what authorities say is a “major marine incident” that has caused “mass casualty” in Connecticut.

item.title: US close to agreeing on long-range missiles for Ukraine; delivery to take months
Suspected homicide victim ID'd 31 years after remains found by kids
item.description: Human remains discovered by children in 1993 south of Indianapolis have been identified as a man from South Carolina, authorities said.

item.title: Israel-Gaza live updates: Hostage families vow fresh cease-fire demonstrations
item.description: As the Israel-Hamas war continues, the latest round of cease-fire discussions appears to have reached an impasse.

item.title: Watch live: Tom Tugendhat promises ‘reset’ as he launches Conservative Party leadership campaign
Paraguay finally gets sex ed classes, but many worry about the lessons
item.description: Paraguay schools will start teaching sex ed, but the lessons have sexual health educators and feminists in a panic. Conservative lobbyists are thrilled.

item.title: Police investigating 5 consecutive shooting incidents on Washington highway
item.description: Police are investigating five separate shootings that occurred consecutively on Interstate 5 in Washington, authorities said.

item.title: Elon Musk defies X ban in Brazil by beaming app from space
Researchers find evidence that large sharks may be hunting each other
item.description: Researchers discovered the first known case of a porbeagle shark likely being killed by a large shark predator, raising questions about whether this rare instance represents a larger trend.

item.title: Pope opens Asia odyssey with stop in Indonesia to rally Catholics
item.description: Pope Francis has arrived in Indonesia to start the longest trip of his pontificate

item.title: Giant python caught swallowing even bigger python alive in world first
Breast cancer rising among Asian American and Pacific Islander women
item.description: Asian American and Pacific Islander women once had a relatively low rate of breast cancer diagnoses. Now, researchers are scrambling to understand what's changed.

item.title: WATCH: Van narrowly misses being hit by oncoming train at crossing
item.description: Eyewitness video captures the moment a van breached a train crossing gate in Virginia, narrowly avoided an oncoming train.

item.title: Donald Trump's Nephew Drops S-Bomb On MSNBC During Searing Takedown Of Uncle
Almost 130 killed in attempted prison escape in Congo, authorities say
item.description: Officials in the Democratic Republic of the Congo say at least 129 people were killed, mostly in a stampede, during an attempted prison escape in Kinshasa.
